Greek outfit Asteras Tripoli have already surpassed their previous best by reaching the group stage of the competition.

In the last two seasons they have got to the third qualifying round, with their appearance in this year's Europa League only their third-ever appearance in the competition.

The full fixture list for the group stage is due to be finalised an hour after the draw takes place, with matches set for September 18, October 2 and 23, November 6 and 27 and December 11.

